diff:1623395983:1623395769:=132c132%0a%3c Theoretically one whale, if they are fast, could time their buys and buy up all of the coins the instant they get dropped every month.  To prevent this, we are instituting a max purchase that is equal to 1/(golden ratio squared) which is around [[https://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=1%252F%25281.6180339887498948482045868343656381177203091798057628621354486227052604628189024497072072041893911374%255E2%2529|38.1966%25]] of the outstanding Tian.  The golden ratio squared is actually more often found in nature than the golden ratio itself [[https://www.goldennumber.net/golden-ratio-myth/|#]].  Whales can still buy up 90%25, or even 99%25 or more of the outstanding Tian; it will just cost them more to do so.  To buy 90%25 of the coins would take 5 separate buys, to buy 99%25 would take a total of 10 buys, to buy 99.9%25 would take a total of 15 buys, etc; and each buy costs more than the last because each buy raises the price of the token.%0a---%0a> Theoretically one whale, if they are fast, could time their buys and buy up all of the coins the instant they get dropped every month.  To prevent this, we are instituting a max purchase that is equal to 1/(golden ratio squared) which is around [[https://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=1%252F%25281.6180339887498948482045868343656381177203091798057628621354486227052604628189024497072072041893911374%255E2%2529|38.1966%25]] of the outstanding Tian.  The golden ratio squared is actually more often the one found in nature [[https://www.goldennumber.net/golden-ratio-myth/|#]].  Whales can still buy up 90%25, or even 99%25 or more of the outstanding Tian; it will just cost them more to do so.  To buy 90%25 of the coins would take 5 separate buys, to buy 99%25 would take a total of 10 buys, to buy 99.9%25 would take a total of 15 buys, etc; and each buy costs more than the last because each buy raises the price of the token.%0a
