diff:1623178422:1623178299:=27c27%0a%3c **Use Case:** Hedging against other assets' price volatility.  However unlike Tether, the price can and likely will rise versus the dollar. Tian should resist following market trends like those seen by leading cryptocurrencies, by adjusting the number of new coins minted based on volume traded.  Typically volume is high when price is high, and in these periods Tian mints more to keep price stable.  Typically when price is low volume is low, and Tian mints less during this time to keep prices up.  Tian can also be very easily traded, and as a standard token it might have very high merchant acceptance rate.  Tian can replace fiat checking deposits, savings deposits, and even commodities like gold in order to hedge against National Currency inflation and, at the same time, Crypto Market volatility.%0a---%0a> **Use Case:** Hedging against other assets' price volatility.  However unlike Tether, the price can and likely will rise versus the dollar. Tian should resist following market trends like those seen by leading cryptocurrencies, by adjusting the number of new coins minted based on volume traded.  Typically volume is high when price is high, and in these periods Tian mints more to keep price stable.  Typically when price is low volume is low, and Tian mints less during this time to keep prices up.  Tian can also be very easily traded and as a token might have very high merchant acceptance rate.  Tian can replace fiat checking deposits, savings deposits, and even commodities like gold in order to hedge against National Currency inflation and, at the same time, Crypto Market volatility.%0a
