diff:1623009142:1623008849:=22c22%0a%3c The basic premise of Tian Token is the embodiment of a solution to the "Inflation Conundrum" in Economics.  Expansion of the money supply is necessary to support a growing economy, however this is always at the expense of those holding the currency.  The amount of new money created devalues the currency holders value.  One common workaround is investing; because some of that newly created money is going into new ventures (aka [[https://knowyourmeme.com/memes/stonks|Stonks]]), and thus currency holders can convert some of their currency into ownership of these ventures thus gaining a return that can be similar to the expansion of the money supply.  Another workaround is using the currency to buy commodities that have a lower or fixed emission like gold.  Both of these solutions require trading your currency for something else, and then converting it back into currency to spend - therefore these solutions are not ideal.%0a---%0a> The basic premise of Tian Token is the embodiment of a solution to the "Inflation Conundrum" in Economics.  Expansion of the money supply is necessary to support a growing economy, however this is always at the expense of those holding the currency.  The amount of new money created devalues the currency holders value.  One common workaround is investing; because some of that newly created money is going into new ventures (aka [[https://knowyourmeme.com/memes/stonks|Stonks]]), and thus currency holders can convert some of their currency into ownership of these ventures thus gaining a return that can be similar to the expansion of the money supply.  Another workaround is using the currency to buy commodities that have a more mellowed or fixed emission like gold.  Both of these solutions require trading your currency for something else, and then converting it back into currency to spend - therefore these solutions are not ideal.%0a
